== 概要 ==
To format references to comic books in a consistent and legible manner.

以一致、清楚的方式把對漫畫書的引用格式化。

== 參數 ==
For a comic book with one creator:

單一創作者的漫畫書：
<nowiki>{{Cite comic
| cartoonist = 
| story = 
| title = 必填
| volume = 
| issue = 
| date = 必填
| publisher = 
| location = 
| page = 
| panel = 
| id =
}}</nowiki>

For a comic book with a writer and separate artist performing both pencilling and inking duties:

作者和畫家為不同人的漫畫書：
<nowiki>{{Cite comic
| writer = 
| artist = 
| story = 
| title = 必填
| volume = 
| issue = 
| date = 必填
| publisher = 
| location = 
| page = 
| panel = 
| id =
}}</nowiki>

For a comic book with separate creators:

擁有不同創作者的漫畫書：
<nowiki>{{Cite comic
| writer = 
| penciller = 
| inker = 
| colorist = 
| letterer = 
| editor = 
| story = 
